query:
query getReusableProfileData {
	profile {
		achRelations {
			isActive
			status
		}
		portfolio {
			brokerAccountsLinked{   
				brokerName
				officialName
				externalAccType
                base64Image
                status
                lastUpdate
                institutionId
                mask
                brokerFilter
			}
			withdrawableAmount
			buyingPower
			settledBalance
			heldawayCash
			mmiCash
			cashBalance
			totalAccountValue
			total
			holdings {
				brokerName
				brokerFilter
				quantity
				averageCost
				marketValue
				temporaryHolding
				type
				id
				quantityAcats
				instrument {
					ticker
					nav
					priceChange	
					percentChange
					isTradable
					type
				    tradability
					shortName
					sponsorDetails {
						sponsor
						sponsorLogoUrl
					}
					id
					name			
					minimumInvestment
				}
			}
		}
	}
}
